      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022R2) holds ISO 9001 certification; version-controlled input decks archived in FDA OSEL repository with MD5 checksums verified at each run.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022R2 is a commercially validated solver with documented QA procedures. All simulation input files were stored under version control (Git, tag v1.4.1) and checksums verified before submission. SQA level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Patch-test and benchmark solutions (NAFEMS LE1, LE10) reproduced to within 0.5% of analytical reference values.",
      "rationale": "Standard NAFEMS benchmark cases LE1 and LE10 were executed in the same solver configuration. Maximum deviation from reference was 0.3%, confirming correct code implementation. Gradation 2 requirements satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
